reviewSnippet.question: What are people saying about shopping in Nanaimo, BC?
reviewSnippet.answerPrompt: This is a review for shopping in Nanaimo, BC:

answer.text: "This consignment store is operated by a young woman with no business sense. She does not behave as though it is a legitimate business.  I would be careful trying to get her to sell anything for you. Her contract is vague and unprofessional, leaving it open so she can do Anything she wants. Never sold any of my top quality, brand name items, even at extremely Low prices.  She handled a customer very rudely in front of me and then complained to me about her! There are a number of consignment stores in town and this is the one I would avoid!"
